But Seo Yu-mi is vehemently against it.

49:44.310 --> 49:46.540
So let's go together and talk to her.

49:46.540 --> 49:47.940
- Me, too?
- Let's go!

49:51.010 --> 49:53.910
This is Hyun-ji from the orphanage.

49:55.340 --> 49:56.560
Is she candidate No.4?

49:56.560 --> 49:58.950
She says she'll only join a major agency.

49:59.910 --> 50:00.910
Jenna.

50:01.780 --> 50:03.370
Let's go together and persuade her.

50:04.090 --> 50:05.700
She scares me.

50:05.980 --> 50:06.900
Jenna!

50:07.590 --> 50:08.540
Jenna!

50:09.060 --> 50:10.060
Excuse me.

50:11.910 --> 50:12.910
I found us

50:13.700 --> 50:14.700
our main

50:14.930 --> 50:15.930
vocalist!

50:32.620 --> 50:34.300
What do you think, Jenna?

50:36.470 --> 50:38.850
About my skills in starting from scratch?

50:42.820 --> 50:45.550
The whole world mocked me,

50:46.300 --> 50:47.980
