50:51.280 --> 50:52.280
See?

50:53.950 --> 50:55.180
We did it.

51:12.940 --> 51:13.940
What the?

51:18.130 --> 51:19.810
Go inside or step aside.

51:23.400 --> 51:24.580
I'm sorry.

51:26.540 --> 51:28.230
I didn't tell you to step back.

51:29.680 --> 51:31.750
Do you always not listen to others?

51:32.560 --> 51:33.560
I'm sorry.

51:35.380 --> 51:36.740
Why are you here?

51:36.880 --> 51:37.880
Oh, well...

51:40.040 --> 51:41.370
I'll tell you this now.

51:41.950 --> 51:44.660
Requests, bribes, appeals, excuses, sob-stories...

51:44.660 --> 51:46.690
They're all things that I hate.

51:46.870 --> 51:48.840
I hate it when the talk gets long.

51:51.100 --> 51:52.100
Here...

52:00.190 --> 52:01.120
Thank you.

52:02.820 --> 52:04.980
I hope you see our performance well.

52:05.040 --> 52:06.570
That's also a request.

52:06.790 --> 52:08.850
I'm asking you to be fair.

52:09.410 --> 52:11.420
No prejudgment or prejudice.

52:13.550 --> 52:14.550
Okay.

52:16.400 --> 52:17.390
You can go now.

52:17.830 --> 52:18.640
Okay.

52:29.630 --> 52:32.530
CEO Cha must be humane unlike the rumors I heard.

52:32.640 --> 52:34.210
The stage is so proper.

52:34.300 --> 52:36.570
It's a test, but he had a whole stage set up.

52:56.260 --> 52:57.700
By the way,

52:58.400 --> 53:00.010
