53:00.380 --> 53:01.860
That's a killer look.

53:08.990 --> 53:09.990
Oh!

53:11.010 --> 53:12.010
That...

53:12.340 --> 53:15.280
It's what CEO Ma bought us the day we debuted.

53:15.600 --> 53:17.590
I want to show CEO Ma.

53:24.930 --> 53:25.930
Me, too.

53:28.510 --> 53:29.970
Seriously.

53:31.450 --> 53:32.850
He said he'll buy us a diamond ring

53:32.850 --> 53:33.940
when we succeeded.

53:34.100 --> 53:36.840
He made promises and just left like that.

53:47.780 --> 53:48.780
Cot!

53:51.450 --> 53:52.450
Ten!

53:53.000 --> 53:54.000
Can!

53:55.060 --> 53:56.060
