54:32.470 --> 54:33.330
Hey.

54:33.760 --> 54:35.050
Why are you here?

54:36.110 --> 54:38.250
You said all available staff to come.

54:39.200 --> 54:41.130
If you're bored, go practice.

54:41.290 --> 54:42.990
