55:05.430 --> 55:06.440
"Honest"?

55:06.440 --> 55:08.510
There are no more

55:08.510 --> 55:12.130
Lies I made up

55:12.870 --> 55:14.470
I don't know who I am

55:14.510 --> 55:18.460
I knew the answer, but I always lost my way

55:18.920 --> 55:20.970
I didn't want it to be true

55:22.420 --> 55:26.500
Under the twinkling star, the compass was dark

55:26.930 --> 55:29.050
What do you feel?

