If I'm honest

57:25.840 --> 57:28.170
Was that sequence originally there?

57:28.320 --> 57:29.780
No, it wasn't.

57:30.000 --> 57:31.760
I think she put it in because she's good at it.

57:31.780 --> 57:34.310
But it doesn't go with this song, does it?

57:34.340 --> 57:36.160
That's why they need an agency.

57:36.160 --> 57:38.380
We can tone down these things.

57:38.480 --> 57:40.430
